Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但文乃为什么那么净白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.56,0:24:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 哪里晒黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.90,0:24:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果杜拉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.64,0:24:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南关于成果的思考
